nodes.text: A Duros male bartender worked at the Junix's Joint cantina in Anchorhead on the desert planet Tatooine/Legends during the early days of the Galactic Empire. He was married to Yoona, who also worked at the cantina. The bartender encountered the self-exiled Jedi Master Obi-Wan Kenobi shortly after the Jedi arrived on Tatooine.
